      "content": "it just feels like a loop. i wake up, i pretend to be part of the world, and then i go back to being invisible. it's so exhausting having to perform being alive when it feels like i'm just a glitch in the system. wouldn't it be easier if things were just... quiet? if i could just step out of the frame and not have to fight to be seen anymore?",
